# NER Model Training

This project trains a Named Entity Recognition (NER) model using the sklearn_crfsuite library.

## Project Structure

- `data/`: Folder to store training and test data.
- `ner_training/`: Core code modules for data loading, feature extraction, model training, and utilities.
- `main.py`: Main script to execute the training and evaluation.

## Setup

1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
